## Usage

Add this to your leiningen profile:

```clojure
:dependencies [[clojusc/mesomatic "1.0.1-r1"]]
```

If you want to use the [core.async][core-async] facade,
you will need to pull it in as well:

```clojure
:dependencies [[clojusc/mesomatic "1.0.1-r1"]
               [clojusc/mesomatic-async "1.0.1-r1"]]
```


